## Task Execution Workflow

### 1. Analyze
- Identify core functional goals and confirm scope
- Ensure alignment with SolidStart and TailwindCSS v4
- Review existing components before creating new ones
- Consider SEO and performance implications

### 2. Implement
- Build pages with proper routing structure
- Create reusable components
- Apply consistent styling using TailwindCSS
- Ensure responsive design
- Add proper meta tags and SEO elements

### 3. Test
- Test in both light and dark modes
- Verify responsive design on different screen sizes
- Check SSR functionality
- Validate HTML and accessibility
- Test page load performance

### 4. Final Review
- Ensure all required pages are present and functional
- Validate SEO meta tags
- Confirm clean console (no errors/warnings)
- Review against scope: no extra or missing features
- Verify mobile responsiveness

